Package client

Class Summary
Job Interface that defines a job to be executed remotely.
TspClient Computes an optimal solution to the Travelling Salesman Problem on a remote machine and displays the solution in a GUI.
TspJob Defines a Travelling Salesman Problem through the generic Job interface
